  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13067540/ski-alberta-inghams-travel-alberta.jpg" alt="Inghams Ski Alberta in partnership with Travel Alberta" data-udi="umb://media/593821aef0c14c4a9a77712a213e1554" /></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">The Canadian province of Alberta is home to some of the most iconic ski holiday destinations in the world – <a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff"><strong>Banff</strong> </a>and <a data-udi="umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75}" title="Lake Louise"><strong>Lake Louise</strong></a>. It is also home to unparalleled natural beauty. The rugged, high Rocky Mountains form the backbone for this magnificent ski region. The wonderful sights are sure to impress you as much as the incredible skiing and snowboarding.</span></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><strong>Banff</strong></span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff"><strong><img src="/media/13067535/ski-alberta-inghams-banff-sunshine-village.jpg" alt="Skiing in Banff" data-udi="umb://media/eaa0f68833dd4d59931d73117549fcd1" /></strong></a></p>
<p>The lively ski resort of Banff is formed of two stunning ski areas: the extensive Sunshine Village and the beautifully tree-lined Mount Norquay. If that wasn’t enough skiing for you, you can also ski in the vast neighbouring resort of Lake Louise using the ‘Tri-Area’ lift pass.</p>
<p>Downtown Banff is the place to stay if you’re looking for a variety of bars and restaurants, while a regular ski bus will take you to one of the many, exciting ski areas. Banff is, without a doubt, one of our most popular ski resorts in Alberta.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f77e79eea2d4582a9acb3c89406dc88}" title="Banff"><strong>Find out more about Banff</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><strong>Lake Louise</strong></span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75}" title="Lake Louise"><strong><img src="/media/13067537/ski-alberta-inghams-lake-louise-massive-ski-area.jpg" alt="Skiing in Lake Louise" data-udi="umb://media/c5e4c410af8641ee83fef8ee807232d6" /></strong></a></p>
<p>With 139 runs, Lake Louise has the prestigious accolade of being the largest ski area in our Alberta programme. It’s a peaceful and tranquil retreat situated in the heart of the Banff National Park. Lake Louise’s beauty is world renowned.</p>
<p>You can enjoy iconic views of the lake from the fabulous Fairmont Chateau hotel. And the surrounding miles of Canadian wilderness ensure epic vistas round every corner. If you’re looking for a beautiful destination for your ski holiday – you’ve found it in Lake Louise.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cf5e06f2ccd4cf8b8f46d06ca905a75}" title="Lake Louise"><strong>Find out more about Lake Louise</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><strong>Jasper</strong></span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/bfa04f44790c46849e2845718190cf27" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfa04f44790c46849e2845718190cf27}" title="Jasper"><strong><img src="/media/13067536/ski-alberta-inghams-jasper-marmot-basin.jpg" alt="Skiing in Jasper" data-udi="umb://media/de9222ddc5444aaeb0ae69d575578a29" /></strong></a></p>
<p>Possibly the most wild ski resort in our Inghams Ski collection, Jasper is a wildlife lover’s paradise. Situated in the largely untouched Jasper National Park, the Marmot Basin is a small but perfectly formed ski resort. There is a chilled and relaxing atmosphere which is as infectious as it is uncrowded.</p>
<p>We love skiing in Jasper, but the resort is also an incredible place to try alternative winter activities such as dog-sledding, wildlife safaris and cross-country skiing. Jasper is a winter wonderland!</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/bfa04f44790c46849e2845718190cf27" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfa04f44790c46849e2845718190cf27}" title="Jasper"><strong>Find out more about Jasper</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span class="geolocation-title location-text"><strong>Canada Month – Special Offer</strong></span></p>
<p><strong><img src="/media/13067538/ski-alberta-inghams-lake-louise-ski-area-incredible-scenery.jpg" alt="Canada Month Special Offer" data-udi="umb://media/66abc96a9566476e92a4753a42134fe2" /></strong></p>
<p>As part of our special Canada Month we’re offering our guests the opportunity to ski in Alberta for less. We have a 20% reduction on the Tri-Area lift pass for Banff and Lake Louise. And we are offering £50 per person off the following selected hotels in Banff:</p>
<ul>
<li><span class="geolocation-title"><a data-udi="umb://document/c5a8431a4b9c4e3fb820365f26d278bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5a8431a4b9c4e3fb820365f26d278bb}" title="Banff Inn Hotel">The Banff Inn Hotel</a>, 3.5*</span></li>
<li><span class="geolocation-title"><a data-udi="umb://document/d004f6b2777e4359b8b451a792433e6a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d004f6b2777e4359b8b451a792433e6a}" title="Caribou Lodge">The Caribou Lodge</a>, 4*</span></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p>Our limited time offer ends on the 30 April 2018 – make sure you book your holiday to Alberta soon.</p>
